nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE FORECAST TO BECOME A TROPICAL STORM AGAIN BY SUNDAY...
summary: ...HENRIETTE FORECAST TO BECOME A TROPICAL STORM AGAIN BY SUNDAY... As of 11:00 PM HST Fri Aug 08 the center of Henriette was located near 20.7, -145.7 with movement WNW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1009 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
